  "texts": [
    "Following HelpSteer2 (Wang et al., 2024b), we assign 3-5 annotators per task to reduce subjectivity and ensure more balanced feedback across model responses.",
    "We collaborate with a data annotation vendor, Scale AI, to recruit annotators for General, STEM, and Coding tasks.",
    "STEM and Coding tasks have stricter inclusion criteria, requiring annotators to have relevant qualifications, such as undergraduate degrees in related fields or software engineering experience.",
    "These tasks, along with their associated prompts and responses, are conducted in English only.",
    "For Multilingual tasks, we partner with a separate vendor, Translated."
  ],
